{"type":null,"faqId":10153,"title":"G6-U00设置飞行模式","answer":"&nbsp;\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（1）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">屏幕，点击<b>设置</b>，点击<b>飞行模式</b>开关，打开或者关闭飞行模式。在飞行模式下，无线网络不可用。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（2）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">可以在通知栏，快速打开或者关闭飞行模式。<span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\"><span>（3）<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:'微软雅黑','sans-serif';\">长按电源键，在弹出的选项菜单中，可以设置打开或者关闭飞行模式。<span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"732","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396603530000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"飞行模式","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}